{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Client.postMessage()","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/API/Client/postMessage","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Client\"><code>Client</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>プロパティ</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Client/frameType\"><code>frameType</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Client/id\"><code>id</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Client/type\"><code>type</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Client/url\"><code>url</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>メソッド</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><em><code>postMessage()</code></em></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p><span class=\"seoSummary\"><strong><code>postMessage()</code></strong> は <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Client\"><code>Client</code></a> インターフェイスのメソッドで、サービスワーカーがクライアント (<a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Window\"><code>Window</code></a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Worker\"><code>Worker</code></a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/SharedWorker\"><code>SharedWorker</code></a>) にメッセージを送信することができます。 メッセージは、 <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/ServiceWorkerContainer\" title=\"navigator.serviceWorker\"><code>navigator.serviceWorker</code></a> の \"<code>message</code>\" イベントで受信されます。</span></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"構文","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><var>client</var>.postMessage(<var>message</var>[, <var>transfer</var>]);\n<var>client</var>.postMessage(<var>message</var>[, { transfer }]);\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameters","title":"引数","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"message\"><code><var>message</var></code></dt>\n <dd>クライアントに送信するメッセージです。これは、任意の<a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Web_Workers_API/Structured_clone_algorithm\">複製可能な構造化型</a>にすることができます。</dd>\n <dt id=\"transfer\"><code><var>transfer</var></code> <span class=\"badge inline optional\">省略可</span></dt>\n <dd>メッセージとともに<a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Transferable\">転送</a>されるオブジェクトのシーケンスです。 これらのオブジェクトの所有権は宛先側に与えられ、送信側では使用できなくなります。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"return_value","title":"返値","isH3":true,"content":"<p><code>undefined</code>。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>サービスワーカーからクライアントへのメッセージの送信</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'fetch'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token parameter\">event</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  event<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">waitUntil</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">async</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// クライアントにアクセスできない場合は、早期に終了します。</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// 例えば、クロスオリジンの場合。</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">!</span>event<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>clientId<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// クライアントを取得します。</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> client <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">await</span> clients<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">get</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>event<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>clientId<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// クライアントを取得できない場合は、早期に終了します。</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// 例えば、閉じている場合。</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">!</span>client<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// クライアントにメッセージを送信します。</span>\n    client<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">postMessage</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      msg<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"私はあなたからフェッチされましたよ！\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      url<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> event<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>request<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>url\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p>そのメッセージの受け取り</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>navigator<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>serviceWorker<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'message'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token parameter\">event</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>event<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>data<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>msg<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> event<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>data<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>url<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"仕様書","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">仕様書</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">状態</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">備考</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/ServiceWorker/#dom-client-postmessage-message-options\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Service Workers<br><small lang=\"ja\">postMessage() の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-wd\">草案</span></td>\n   <td>初回定義</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.Client.postMessage","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/Client/postMessage/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\">\n<p></p><p></p>\n</div>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"構文","id":"syntax"},{"text":"例","id":"examples"},{"text":"仕様書","id":"specifications"},{"text":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility"}],"summary":"postMessage() は Client インターフェイスのメソッドで、サービスワーカーがクライアント (Window, Worker, SharedWorker) にメッセージを送信することができます。 メッセージは、 navigator.serviceWorker の \"message\" イベントで受信されます。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Client.postMessage()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Client.postMessage()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Client.postMessage()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/api/client/postmessage","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/api/client/postmessage/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/Client","title":"Client"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/Client/postMessage","title":"Client.postMessage()"}],"pageTitle":"Client.postMessage() - Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}